snippet.title: The Messy Coder
snippet.description:
I created this new YouTube channel to upload fun (I hope) game dev tutorials, aimed at us beginners who just like to enjoy themselves and get messy with code.

If you have any requests for tutorials or just want to chat, feel free to send me a message or put a comment in one of the videos. 

I want to send out a massive thank you to everyone who takes the time to watch, like, comment and subscribe. It really means a lot and it's a lot of fun talking about game development and gaming with you all.
